description: The Journal of Open Research Software (JORS) features peer reviewed Software Metapapers describing research software with high reuse potential. Equally importantly, the software and the papers will be citable, and reuse will be tracked.JORS also publishes full-length research papers that cover different aspects of creating, maintaining and evaluating open source research software.
